    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m listing my reliable ride that\u2019s been such a joy to own. It runs super smoothly and has been really well-loved, making it perfect for your daily commutes or fun weekend road trips! It\u2019s in solid shape and totally ready for its next adventure with a new owner. I\u2019m sad to see it go, but I know you\u2019re going to absolutely love driving it as much as I have. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'm super happy to chat!",
