    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "Offered is a mechanically robust E46 M3, powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six featuring individual throttle bodies and a fully serviced dual-VANOS system. This example features the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission, delivering power to the rear wheels via a factory M Variable Differential Lock. Critical preventative maintenance has been executed, including rear subframe reinforcement and rod bearing replacement, ensuring the chassis remains rigid under load. The suspension retains its telepathic feedback through refreshed bushings and upgraded dampers, while the engine pulls linearly to its 8,000 RPM redline. A driver\u2019s car in every sense, it balances visceral performance with daily usability.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 20
    },
