    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2019 Audi A6 3.0T Premium Plus, finished in a timeless Firmament Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and presents beautifully. The exterior paint retains a deep luster, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the hood and one small, professionally touched-up scratch on the passenger door\u2014typical for a car of this mileage. The 19-inch alloy wheels are wrapped in Continental tires with plenty of tread remaining, though there is a very light curb mark on the rear driver-side rim. Inside, the Valcona leather interior is in excellent shape; the seats are firm and free of tears, with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All technology features, including the MMI Touch Response system and the Virtual Cockpit, are fully operational. Mechanically, the car is solid. It features a complete service history from authorized dealerships, including a recent 40,000-mile major service and a fresh oil change. The engine runs quietly, and the Quattro all-wheel-drive system provides a confident, smooth ride in all weather conditions. This is a smoke-free, pet-free vehicle that offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
