    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "This expertly maintained vehicle represents a distinguished opportunity for the discerning motorist. Characterized by reliable mechanical performance and a well-preserved exterior, this unit has undergone a comprehensive assessment to ensure it meets our exacting standards for roadworthiness and comfort. The interior cabin reflects a high level of care, offering a sophisticated environment for both driver and passengers. This is a premier selection for those seeking a vehicle that balances enduring capability with a commanding presence on the road.",
      "price": 32450.0,
