    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_14_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_14",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-maintained\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 34500.0,
