    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sorted 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S. This 996.2 wide-body utilizes the 3.6L M96 flat-six, putting power down through a G96 6-speed manual and a viscous-coupling AWD system. Crucially, the IMS bearing has been upgraded to a ceramic dual-row unit, and the RMS is bone dry. The chassis features the C4S-specific reinforced subframe and 'Big Red' four-piston monoblock Brembo calipers. Suspension remains tight with Bilstein B6 dampers and factory-spec geometry. While the exterior shows honest road wear consistent with its mileage, the drivetrain is optimized for performance with no bore scoring detected. A driver's car that prioritizes mechanical integrity and analog feedback.",
